No. 09-38 (R46-009). Health Care Service Corporation, Petitioner v. Juli A. Pollitt, et al. 559 U.S. 965, 130 S. Ct. 1574,

176 L. Ed. 2d 157,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 1901. February 24, 2010.

The writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Seventh Circuit in the above-entitled case was dismissed today pursuant to this Court’s Rule 46.1.
